So far in the ShadowIRCd 2.5 branch:
* Fixed rogue +L target bug
* Fixed -L * * bug
* Fixed immunity bugs
* Modechanges for users set by servers are now propigated
* Added initial support for persistant clients. (not recommended for use yet)
* Added technical/network administrator flags.
* Added cmode +a -- auditorium.
* Fixed topic bugs
* Server to Server challenge authentication removed (unstable)
* Modernized ircd.conf slightly.
* Removed redundant notice flags, changed +e (identified) to +r.
* Added umode +X -- invisiblity.
